Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你可别迟到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄关的这个你别碰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别放进冰箱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 你很啰嗦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1签 不平衡邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一般垃圾）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 麦男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊 快乐好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着你在四月份会有最佳的运势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并可期待美好的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是别太期待的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺清心寡欲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够参加今天的入学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示你至少有过一次好运不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指抽中入学的签啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 搞不好我的好运全都用在那上头了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请确认您的车票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种不祥的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信者得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点安慰效果都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生起立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜各位入学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立桥院高中已创校130年 拥有5000名学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其历史与规模皆相当辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位新生能好好发挥各自的过人体力、智力与意志力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也期待各位的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰卡士达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部出席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该也没人会在入学典礼就请假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一下子学生会应该会开始广播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前可以自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用一一自我介绍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个你们自己做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的年纪已经不需要听人发号施令了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师竟然一点干劲都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分班之后才发现抽到烂签
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是好签
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师他不看名册就喊出了大家的名字 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能大家很想认为自己运气好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得与自己无关似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能入学我就很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不奢望更多的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个“快乐好运”在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那样叫我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查个资料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蕈类）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想拜托她别再买些莫名其妙的东西回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟那些是在哪里？跟谁？又是花了多少钱买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算姊姊那个德性 应该不至于是自己去采的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心的咖啡色 又皱巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶端带着红色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形状为球形或不规则形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细部软而白 多为圆柱状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多生长于春天的针叶林带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度为5~8公分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极稀罕能长超过15公分 这就是鹿花菌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉字写成“赤熊编笠茸”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带有剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要以水煮过 并避免吸入含有毒性的蒸气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同青年的气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道温和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同脸颊红润的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种风味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同畅游神仙世界般玄妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你晓得蕈类就是菌类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孢子羞怯地长成菌丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菌丝合体后成为原基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原基成长后就是菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯而有力的生长过程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何迟疑与踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以孢子不断繁衍的高等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了这种感觉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 蕈类就会成为你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为你的导师 你的伴侣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时常相伴左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位应该都已经晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将进行抽签
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家各抽一张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面显示的数字与文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表在这接下来的一年里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须夺取的职位 以及你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(508 会长 游泳池）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(006 会议 音乐教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(027 书记 烹饪教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我只认识你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作会有新的邂逅就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又说这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽好签后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请火速前往签上记载的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 快乐好运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请勿吵闹 迅速行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发现值得期待的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的一年真教人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烹饪教室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各团体成员确认完毕后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将举行练习赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级生请担任各场比赛的评审
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（烹饪教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（世界的蕈类）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也抽中烹饪教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 说不定只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？时乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朝雾小牧 担任会计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是秋山时乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我好像是学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘泉 我是副会长 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是榎本千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任书记 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到第一战就跟你对上了 秋山时乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就怨叹自己不走运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…同伴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是上石神井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上石神井莲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们读橡实山幼稚园白兔班 去远足的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你拉走老师 慢吞吞地跑去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我做什么都是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是背诵地址 用汉字写名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连加法也是我上石神井莲子第一个学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你进了厕所 一直拖拖拉拉的不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是小莲子啊 尿裤子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上石神井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过 不准叫我“同学”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我莲子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸部很恶心耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 莲子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将你送入地狱的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的比赛为热身赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩将不列入记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间为60分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘数无上限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的规定就是必须使用指定的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输赢由会长判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食材就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头混有带毒的种类 所以必须谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的关键就在于如何选择蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方都准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网柄牛肝菌 风味A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬菇 风味同样为A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用电脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“用蕈类烹煮料理”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规定只有这一项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 你看着好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边有时乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个含有α鹅膏蕈素与β鹅膏蕈素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一株就能让一名成人致死的鳞柄白鹅膏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别名“死亡天使”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝膜菌 通称“黑大国”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是蕈类专家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是喜欢蕈类罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点走火入魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有得忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要像她那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然一点用也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要我吃的话 我还蛮擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为讨厌吃蕈类 会很讨厌吃它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上没人想知道你的饮食偏好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我就此倒下 不就正中秋山时乃的下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做出能拉大差距的料理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木、健司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在\N在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要学会世上最高境界的这本三颗星的食谱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 莲子小姐很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将切成两半的螯虾准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等平底锅内的奶油熔化后 将螯虾放上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮到半熟时从锅内取出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后将铆钉菇放入锅内 吸取螯虾及奶油的风味…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成她可以过目不忘？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 她很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他两人只是听从指示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就能做得那么流畅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有命令就无法动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这就是填鸭教育的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲子小姐更厉害的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲子小姐\N莲子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让铆钉菇吸取风味后\N让铆钉菇吸取风味后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该如何处理螯虾？\N该如何处理螯虾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螯虾是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她只记得住3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是惊奇的3分钟默背术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很懂 不过真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会对人家感到佩服或望着人家出神吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你帮我拿个盘子对你来说太困难了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈类用水冲洗会让美味流失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是要稍微泡一下 还是用湿布擦拭就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么烹煮这些蕈类？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出点子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量保持原味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人品尝到不同的风味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤、炖汤、或是跟饭一起煮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是法国料理的大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很清楚自己并不具备那样的厨艺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以倒不如制作简单的菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场练习赛颇出人意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你安排好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为主题是蕈类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我早就知道她对蕈类特别了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我为什么要故意这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是为了赖在你家不走的那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 你应该也明白抽签是很神圣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的签运的确都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的 你干嘛喂时乃吃香菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害她发动了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时乃太贪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来以为这种时候没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出马脚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们桌上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的 什么都没有 空荡荡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山时乃 你也不过是这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的团队如同踩到自己丢的香蕉皮滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又遇到午后雷阵雨 没能准时赴约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此搞砸了重要的商谈与人际关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只有这种程度 也暗示着你们未来之灰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有5分钟 你做得出什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算来洗锅子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕈类也只剩有毒的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿花菌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含有单甲基胺毒素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人出现呕肚腹泻等症状后致死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只要藉由煮沸将有毒成分完全去除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何蕈类比它还美味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在欧洲还被视为告知春天到来的蕈类 相当珍贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 我就让你们连半道菜都做不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木、健司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在\N在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得来表现一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由马铃薯做成的Knoedel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将SteinPilz与Pfifferlinge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}SteinPilz：德文“牛肝菌”；Pfifferlinge：德文“鸡油蕈”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切碎了加在里头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knoedel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德文的丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她晓得会长是日德混血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意拍马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山时乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保证这道料理的安全吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白这种蕈可以食用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们能保证已完全除去毒素了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是学生会长发生万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是会长的职责所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长 既然你都吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来宣布成绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣布秋山时乃队获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的可是三颗星食谱加上综合日西中式口味的大餐耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还会输给那么寒酸的一小盘菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意你的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于食材的鲜度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算花了再多技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是比不上食材原本具备的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点不在于煮出法国或是中华料理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要做出蕈类料理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山队将新鲜食材的力量发挥得淋漓尽致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他们获胜的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底惨败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣布比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小律对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 榎本千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候回来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么久了？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为你还待在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不通知我一声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我判断没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不再是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意娶我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.78,0:24:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来有什么精彩表现？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们 而是秋山同学他们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠揍！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.48,0:24:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会认为秋山时乃才是“不签”的女主角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.45,0:24:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要说的话 我认为会长才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠揍…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.22,0:24:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角居然是学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:24:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不过是长得漂亮了点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.59,0:25:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身是谜 胸部颇大 似乎有什么过去之类的点点点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不平衡抽签 下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.86,0:25:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狂风巨浪！立桥院高中学生会执行部」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们也会登场

